{"word":"暗","detail":[{"title":"基本字义解释","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"● "},{"type":"strong","content":"暗"},{"type":"span","content":"ànㄢˋ","class":["pinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎ 不亮，没有光，与“明”相对：黑"},{"type":"span","content":"暗","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"。"},{"type":"span","content":"暗","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"淡（ａ．不光明；ｂ．喻景象悲惨）。阴"},{"type":"span","content":"暗","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"。"},{"type":"span","content":"暗","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"无天日。"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎ 不公开的，隐藏不露的："},{"type":"span","content":"暗","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"藏。"},{"type":"span","content":"暗","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"号。"},{"type":"span","content":"暗","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"杀。"},{"type":"span","content":"暗","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"娼。"},{"type":"span","content":"暗","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"沟。"},{"type":"span","content":"暗","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"含（做事、说话包含某种意思而未明白说出）。"},{"type":"span","content":"暗","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"流（ａ．流动的地下水；ｂ．喻潜伏的思想倾向或社会动态）。明察"},{"type":"span","content":"暗","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"访。"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎ 愚昧，糊涂："},{"type":"span","content":"暗","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"昧。"},{"type":"span","content":"暗","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"弱（愚昧软弱）。兼听则明，偏信则"},{"type":"span","content":"暗","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"。"}]]},{"title":"同义词、反义词","content":[]},{"title":"英文翻译","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"dark; obscure; in secret, covert"}]]},{"title":"详细字义解释","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"◎ "},{"type":"strong","content":"暗"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"àn","class":["pinyin"]},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"img","content":"","class":["sound"]},{"type":"text","content":" "}],[{"type":"span","content":"〈形容词〉","class":["parts"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"(1) (形声。从日,音声。本义:昏暗)"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(2) 同本义。与“明”相对"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"暗,日无光也。——《说文》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"日中光明,故其出入时光暗,故大。——《论衡·说日》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"体之感何自起?曰,起于远近之比例,明暗之掩映。——蔡元培《图画》"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(3) 又如:昏暗(光线不足);暗中摸索(在黑暗中寻找探索)"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(4) 昏昧,愚昧;不明白"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"上暗则政险。——《荀子·天率》"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(5) 又如:暗昧(真假不明;暧昧,含糊不清);暗主(昏庸的君主)"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(6) 隐秘"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"别有幽愁暗恨生,此时无声胜有声。——白居易《琵琶行》"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(7) 又如:暗记儿;暗号"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(8) 地下。如:暗河;暗沟(地下的排水沟)"}]]},{"title":"词性变化","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"◎ "},{"type":"strong","content":"暗"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"àn","class":["pinyin"]},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"img","content":"","class":["sound"]},{"type":"text","content":" "}],[{"type":"span","content":"〈副词〉","class":["parts"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"(1)  默默地[do not say a word;keep silent]"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"暗算乡程隔数州,欲归无计泪空流。——杜荀鹤《旅寓诗》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"孺人半夜觉寝,促有光暗诵。—— 归有光《先妣事略》"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(2)  又如:暗诵(默诵,背诵);暗数(默默记数);暗写(默写)"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(3)  秘密;暗中"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"曹节王甫,暗杀太后。——《后汉书·宦者传》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"孤犬无猛噬,长箭不暗射。——元好问《驱猪行》"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎ "},{"type":"strong","content":"暗"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"àn","class":["pinyin"]},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"img","content":"","class":["sound"]},{"type":"text","content":" "}],[{"type":"span","content":"〈名词〉","class":["parts"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"(1)  天黑"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"车驾逼暗乃还,漏已尽。——《晋书·职官志》"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(2)  黑夜。如:暗夜(黑夜);暗风(黑夜的风)"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎ "},{"type":"strong","content":"暗"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"àn","class":["pinyin"]},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"img","content":"","class":["sound"]},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"span","content":"〈动词〉","class":["parts"]},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"使昏暗"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"大车扬飞尘,亭午暗阡陌。——李白《古风》"}]]},{"title":"常用词组","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"暗暗"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"àn’àn","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"(1)内心知道或感到但不声张地"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"暗暗吃了一惊"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"(2)不露声色地;暗中"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"他暗暗发誓要为死去的朋友报仇"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"暗娼"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"ànchāng","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"私娼,在某些国家和地区指未得官方许可的暗地里卖淫的妓女"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"暗场"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"ànchǎng","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"不在舞台上表演,只在台词中交代,使观众会意的戏剧情节"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"暗潮"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"àncháo","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"暗流。未在表面显露,暗中形成趋势的势力"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"暗沉沉"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"ànchénchén","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"形容暗而阴沉(多指无色)"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"用旧了的牛皮箭筒,绵甲上的黄铜护心镜,都在暗沉沉的夜影中闪着亮光。——姚雪垠《李自成》"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"stron